{"HYKE":[{"def":"See Haik, and Huke.","pos":""}],"HYKSOS":[{"def":"A dynasty of Egyptian kings, often called the Shepherd kings, of foreign origin, who, according to the narrative of Manetho, ruled for about 500 years, forming the XVth and XVIth dynasties.","pos":""},{"def":"A large Wealden dinosaur from the Tilgate Forest, England.","pos":""}]}